---
import StatsSection from "./StatsSection.astro";
import SocialButtons from "./ui/SocialButtons.astro";
---

<section class="w-full py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-background items-center px-4">
  <div class="container px-4 md:px-6 m-auto">
    <div class="grid gap-10 sm:px-10 md:gap-16 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div
          class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-muted py-1 text-primary font-medium text-2xl"
        >
          Sobre Nosotros
        </div>
        <h2
          class="mb-8 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-none tracking-normal text-gray-900 md:text-6xl md:tracking-tight"
        >
          Impulsamos tu negocio al siguiente nivel
        </h2>
        <p
          class="max-w-[600px] text-muted-foreground md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed text-gray-600 xl:text-xl/relaxed"
        >
          Somos una agencia creativa que ofrece servicios integrales de
          marketing digital, diseño web y desarrollo de aplicaciones. Nuestro
          objetivo es ayudarte a alcanzar tus metas y hacer crecer tu negocio.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start space-y-4">
        <div
          class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-muted py-1 text-2xl text-primary"
        >
          Nuestros Valores
        </div>
        <p
          class="mx-auto max-w-[700px] text-muted-foreground md:text-xl/relaxed text-gray-600"
        >
          Nos guiamos por principios de excelencia, innovación y compromiso con
          nuestros clientes. Trabajamos en equipo para brindar soluciones
          creativas y efectivas que impulsen el crecimiento de tu negocio.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-yellow-500"
            >
              <path
                d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z"
              ></path>
              <path
                d="m12 15-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z"
              ></path>
              <path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0"></path>
              <path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-foreground font-medium">Innovación</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-yellow-500"
            >
              <path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-foreground font-medium">Trabajo en Equipo</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-yellow-500"
            >
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"></circle>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"></circle>
            </svg>
            <span class="font-medium">Enfoque en Resultados</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-6 w-6 text-yellow-500"
            >
              <path d="M7 10v12"></path>
              <path
                d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2h0a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-foreground font-medium">Compromiso</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <SocialButtons />
    </div>
    <StatsSection />
  </div>
</section>
